    "summary": "Somalia's Minister of Communications and Technology, Mohamed Adam Maalim Soomaali, held a bilateral meeting with World Bank Vice President Sangbu Kim on the sidelines of the WSIS+20 Forum in Geneva to discuss digital transformation cooperation.",
    "content": "Mohamed Adam Maalim Soomaali, Somalia's Minister of Communications and Technology, met with Sangbu Kim, Vice President for Digital Transformation at the World Bank, during the WSIS+20 high-level forum in Geneva, Switzerland. The meeting focused on strengthening collaboration between Somalia and the World Bank in the digital sector.\n\nThe WSIS+20 Forum marks two decades since the World Summit on the Information Society, and provides a platform for global leaders to assess progress and set new targets for digital development. For Somalia, participating at this level signals growing international engagement in its technological advancement.\n\nMinister Soomaali outlined Somalia's priorities for digital infrastructure, including expanding internet access, improving cybersecurity, and supporting tech entrepreneurship. The World Bank's digital transformation division has supported similar initiatives in other post-conflict countries, offering technical expertise and funding.\n\nThis meeting comes as Somalia works to rebuild its communications network after decades of conflict, with mobile money and digital services already playing a critical role in the economy. For the Somali diaspora, better connectivity means improved access to banking, remittances, and communication with relatives back home.\n\nThe partnership could accelerate Somalia's digital agenda, potentially leading to more reliable internet services and new e-government platforms. Such developments would directly benefit Somalis abroad who rely on digital channels for business, education, and family ties.\n\nRead the original report from Radio Dalsan here: https://radiodalsan.com/2026/07/10/wasiir-soomaali-oo-kulan-la-yeeshay-bangiga-adduunka/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wasiir-soomaali-oo-kulan-la-yeeshay-bangiga-adduunka",
